data.description: BEAUTIFUL POOL HOME in the exclusive gated community of RIVER HILLS COUNTRY CLUB. Enjoy the peace and serenity of this POND LOT single family 3,400+ sqft, 5 bedroom, 4/1 bath, +Loft, 3 car garage, POOL HOME. This home is an entertainer’s dream!  As you pull up to this home you notice the gorgeous curbside appeal with detailed coastal landscaping, and the welcoming covered entry inviting you inside. Upon entering, you are welcomed into a large foyer with high ceilings, beautiful architectural detailing complemented by crown molding flowing throughout the main living space of the home. At the front of the home is a secondary bedroom which easily transforms into the perfect home office. With an open, seamless floor plan, the formal dining room sets the mood for elegance with an evening of luxurious entertaining flowing into the formal living room overlooking the pool. The triple split floor plan with guest rooms and baths placed opposite from the master bedroom with an opulent ensuite bath garden tub, walk-in shower, his & her vanities and walk-in closet with access to pool & lanai.  Amenities abound in this kitchen with ample storage space, all wood cabinetry, granite countertops, all stainless steel appliances, large island with sink and a breakfast bar is the perfect for a party spread, and more!! The family room and  lovely breakfast nook is the ideal place to gather as it overlooks the pool and outdoor oasis. The private secondary guest suite is tucked away with a full size bath. There are two additional secondary bedrooms with spacious closets and a full size bathroom. Upstairs you will find a MASSIVE bonus loft with a full size bath that is great for movie night or entertaining your guests during game night. Step out onto the sun-drenched enclosed patio, and enjoy an afternoon get together with friends and family relaxing and splashing in the pool or escaping to the serenity & peacefulness of a pond view. If you've been looking for a slice of paradise with nature and elegance, LOOK NO MORE! Schedule a showing TODAY!! UPGRADES INCLUDE: UPDATED TILE & LVP; OFFICE LVP & FRENCH DOORS; INTERIOR PAINT; 1/2 BATH - NEW VANITY & TOILET; ALL NEW TOILETS THROUGHOUT;  PLANTATION SHUTTERS; MASTER BATH REMODEL; RANGE, HOOD, FRIDGE & DISHWASHER; NEW OUTDOOR FANS; AC 2020; ROOF 2020/2021; WATER HEATER 2021
